    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// La bridge ritorna JSON parsato in $json. Merge con i parametri Set + costruisce prompt copy.\nconst build = $input.first().json;\nconst src = $('Set lang/concept').first().json;\nconst lang = src.lang;\nconst s = build && build.script ? build.script : { headline:'', specs:[], outro:'' };\nconst specsLine = (s.specs || []).join(' / ');\nconst copy_prompt = `You are the AdOff social copywriter. Brand voice: \"we\" (plural), direct, empathetic, minimal. We leverage the frustration of being BURIED, DROWNED, BOMBARDED by ads on streaming platforms and on every site. Ending feeling: silence / relief in one click.\n\nWrite everything in language code: ${lang}.\n\nCONTEXT (use this video script's TONE and KEYWORDS, do NOT copy verbatim):\n- HEADLINE: ${s.headline}\n- BODY: ${specsLine}\n- OUTRO: ${s.outro}\n\nOUTPUT STRICTLY as JSON with these keys:\n- caption: ONE punchy hook sentence in target language, max 150 chars, ending with soft CTA \"adoff.app\". MUST use a strong frustration verb (Italian: sepolto/invaso/bombardato/soffocato/spazzati; English: buried/drowned/flooded/swallowed; German: begraben/überflutet). NO weak filler like \"niente problemi\" or \"nessun problema\". NO emoji. NO quotes around the string.\n- hashtags: array of EXACTLY 8 hashtag strings, each starting with # and concatenated (no internal spaces, lowercase except brand). EACH hashtag MUST be a REAL natural word or natural compound in language ${lang} — NEVER an English literal when language is not English (forbidden examples in IT: #streamingplatforms #everysite #everywhere #cleanweb). NEVER invented gibberish (forbidden: #bannerofter #adsofter, random mashups). Use real ${lang} vocabulary. ALWAYS include the 2 brand tags #adoff and #adsoff (these stay in English, brand-specific). Valid IT examples: #pubblicità #stopads #navigaresenzapubblicità #adblock #privacy #zeroads. Valid DE: #Werbung #keineWerbung #Adblocker #Privatsphäre.\n- disclosure: ONE short sentence in language ${lang} stating the content is AI-assisted (EU AI Act).\n\nABSOLUTE RULES (output will be filtered, do NOT violate):\n- NEVER mention real brand or platform names (no #youtube #google #facebook #tiktok #instagram #chrome #firefox #safari #edge #opera #amazon #reddit #twitch).\n- NO pricing, NO \"trial\", NO \"15 days\", NO \"paid\", NO \"subscription\".\n- Caption MUST be in language code ${lang} AND contain a frustration verb from the list above.\n- hashtags array MUST have exactly 8 items, all in language ${lang} (except #adoff and #adsoff which are brand tags).\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON, no markdown fences, no commentary.`;\nreturn [{ json: { lang: src.lang, concept: src.concept, build, copy_prompt } }];"
      },
